  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零信任安全架构下的事件驱动流程图。核心是从Aggregate产生事件，最终触发Side Effect，中间要经过Event Store、Reactor和Queue Worker这几个环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先确认一下参与者的顺序：Aggregate是第一个，然后是Event Store、Reactor、Queue、Queue Worker，最后是Side Effect？还有，Queue和Queue Worker是两个独立的参与者吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Queue和Queue Worker要分开。Queue只是存储待处理的任务，Worker是真正执行process的。流程是：Aggregate把事件存到Event Store，然后Reactor订阅并往Queue里push job，Worker从Queue取出并处理，最后去执行Side Effect。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把六个参与者和主流程画出来了：Store Event、Dispatch Event、Push Job、Process Job、Execute Side Effect。接下来需要处理成功和失败的分支逻辑吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Aggregate",
        "Event Store",
        "Reactor",
        "Queue",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Side Effect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要。Side Effect执行完后要返回结果给Worker。如果是Success，Worker要mark job as completed；如果是Failure，则要retry。这两个分支用alt来画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。alt块里画了Success和Failure两个分支：Success时Side Effect返回成功，Worker标记job为completed；Failure时返回失败，Worker触发retry。整个零信任的事件驱动流程应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Side Effect",
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，retry之后应该回到哪里？我看现在Retry Job是Worker发给Queue，但逻辑上应该是重新进入Process Job环节。还有，Mark Job as Completed也应该是Worker发给Queue，不是Worker自己记。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue",
        "Process Job"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正。现在Mark Job as Completed和Retry Job都是Worker发回给Queue的消息，符合实际的消息队列交互模式。retry的逻辑在Queue层处理重新调度，这样整个流程就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue Worker",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
